data.description: Nothing to do but MOVE IN to this beautiful home with all new paint and flooring.  This spacious home features a large living room with picture window to enjoy mountain a neighborhood views, Eat in Kitchen, Dining Room, 2 Bedrooms and 1.5 Baths on the main level and Third Bedroom, Large Family Room, Bath and Laundry Room in lower level. The large back yard is completely fenced.  You will enjoy the large front porch and rear deck and the convenient location of this home.  Just minutes from shopping and historic downtown Luray, Shenandoah National Park and the Shenandoah River.
